{"tid":2196612,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓毛敏感有冇得醫？","createTime":"2020-09-10T04:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T14:42:11.000Z","uid":324785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c97cbb9a406af9d3939d77f5f6d0632d33f0019e","tid":2196612,"uid":324785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"本身讀緊書個陣就發現自己對貓敏感<br />\n試過同短毛貓係一間房仔一個鐘<br />\n佢係籠入面冇掂冇盛乞嗤咳鼻涕眼淚係咁流<br />\n全身痕皮膚又紅要食返治敏速先好啲<br />\n之後就唔敢再同佢地接觸/想玩都帶住個口罩<br />\n有冇話咩方法可以有抗體？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c786343faf562e555488d39323de24cb286141","tid":2196612,"uid":342282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n養和有"},{"pid":"bad445f76359bc33e70d6db92b5c214212cc178f","tid":2196612,"uid":194327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"我呀媽以前去啲auntie 屋企都有對貓毛(長毛波斯)敏感<br />\n佢就算唔同隻貓接觸啲皮膚都會紅同痕。嚴重嘅會流眼水成面紅腫<br />\n<br />\n而家我屋企有兩隻短毛佢又無乜嘢。我哋全日都開住空氣清新機，佢話隻貓一入屋都有痕。但而家養左兩年都無乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔知會唔會慢慢習慣左"},{"pid":"c1d6f327f07bc6b35ea377031b08c8647d0fff5e","tid":2196612,"uid":72952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"好似冇得醫<br />\n不過長期同貓一齊,當係訓練咁,敏感症狀會輕微D"},{"pid":"096ea5464140374975ade73c4c190b941d0189a4","tid":2196612,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"食抗敏藥"},{"pid":"524f83c90b6703ba78c6cf5ea16392e4c7a389c0","tid":2196612,"uid":13368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔係貓毛，係貓囗水<br />\n佢奶毛先令你以為係貓毛"},{"pid":"e87febeb642bacf575be1cfa6665383262519c72","tid":2196612,"uid":48962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1702955c37ab28ef0d78011d432aa01f0463b8a3","tid":2196612,"uid":152254,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score"