.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cd0f99542328992dfe63e6b443c3cd5c6e4e80","tid":2196612,"uid":324785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87febeb642bacf575be1cfa6665383262519c72","tid":2196612,"uid":48962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfd0da579877d469c2d14e8e4fd910a9f6fc433","tid":2196612,"uid":324785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa98a545ec55e9449dc49ec931a2a58f34b69cd0","tid":2196612,"uid":218552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"真係會自動好返 <br />\n我之前都係咁<br />\n成身起風&quot;癩&quot;<br />\n好誇張 <br />\n但養左一年  由同一間房都痕又流鼻水 <br />\n變成間中有起粒粒<br />\n鼻完全無事<br />\n但當然 清潔要做得好好 唔日日拖地都要日日吸塵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"Same尤其是依家轉天氣仲嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有冇話搽啲咩定由佢自己好？"},{"pid":"ed88f661cc0dc0101030c4488415e1ea63786fca","tid":2196612,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"睇過醫生話敏感冇得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916ba608fabd0d55c0bc695099c7d63690a7208b","tid":2196612,"uid":324785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb06f1b9381333989786843082a18e0413ff344c","tid":2196612,"uid":358731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c97cbb9a406af9d3939d77f5f6d0632d33f0019e","tid":2196612,"uid":324785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"本身讀緊書個陣就發現自己對貓敏感<br />\n試過同短毛貓係一間房仔一個鐘<br />\n佢係籠入面冇掂冇盛乞嗤咳鼻涕眼淚係咁流<br />\n全身痕皮膚又紅要食返治敏速先好啲<br />\n之後就唔敢再同佢地接觸/想玩都帶住個口罩<br />\n有冇話咩方法可以有抗體？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:37:26.000Z